OL,3,CWoman spends #10,000 on exercise field
OL,4,Cfor XL bully dogs after legal crackdown
OL,6,FWATCH: A woman from Thanet has spent
OL,7,F#10,000 fencing off a field where XL
OL,8,FBully owners can exercise their dogs
OL,9,Ffor free.
OL,11,FA Kent dog groomer has launched a
OL,12,Fcampaign for a radical rethink of the
OL,13,Frecent legal crackdown on XL bully
OL,14,Ftype dogs.
OL,16,FGail Robertson, from Thanet, says the
OL,17,Fnew requirement to have them
OL,18,Fregistered, neutered and muzzled in
OL,19,Fpublic is "cruel and illogical".
