OL,3,CWoman spends #10,000 on exercise field
OL,4,Cfor XL bully dogs after legal crackdown
OL,6,FGail has responded to the government's
OL,7,Flatest announcement by spending
OL,8,F#10,000 fencing off a field where XL
OL,9,Fbully owners can exercise their dogs
OL,10,Ffor free - unleashed and unmuzzled.
OL,12,FGail said: "If I had the money and the
OL,13,Fspace, I would put 10 fields in.
OL,14,FPeople are willing to travel from
OL,15,Fhours and hours away just to give
OL,16,Ftheir dog that freedom.
