OL,6,F"It needs to be private and it needs
OL,7,Fto be by appointment only, in order to
OL,8,Fremain private. I cannot charge for
OL,9,Fit, or it becomes a business and
OL,10,Fpublic again."
OL,12,FThose who have travelled to the field
OL,13,Fwith their XL bully dogs have
OL,14,Fdescribed the space as a "lifeline".
OL,16,FWhat are the new XL bully rules?
OL,18,FLast week, it became a criminal
OL,19,Foffence to own an XL bully dog in
OL,20,FEngland and Wales without a
OL,21,Fcertificate of exemption.
