OL,6,FAs well as neutering their animals, XL
OL,7,Fbully owners wanting to certify their
OL,8,Fdog as exempt needed to pay an
OL,9,Fapplication fee, hold third party
OL,10,Fpublic liability insurance for their
OL,11,Fpets and ensure the dogs are
OL,12,Fmicrochipped.
OL,14,FIt comes after the government
OL,15,Fintroduced new measures in December
OL,16,Fdictating that XL bullies and be kept
OL,17,Fin secure enough accommodation that
OL,18,Fthey cannot escape.
