OL,6,FIt will be considered a criminal
OL,7,Foffence if owners are not complying
OL,8,Fwith the new rules.
OL,10,FGail has also launched a to Parliament
OL,11,Fonline calling for the repeal of last
OL,12,Fweek's legal measures.
OL,14,FInstead, she wants the focus to be on
OL,15,Fthe owner instead of the dog, with
OL,16,Fpeople required to apply for licences
OL,17,Fthat could be refused for applicants
OL,18,Fassessed as unsuitable - including
OL,19,Fanyone with criminal convictions.
