OL,6,FGail's petition has already attracted
OL,7,Fmore than 100 signatures. If the
OL,8,Fnumber hits 100,000, it could trigger
OL,9,Fa debate in the Commons on the issue.
OL,11,FGail said: "We should be licensing
OL,12,Fpeople. If people had a dog license
OL,13,Fand then they wanted to have a bigger
OL,14,Fdog, they could then prove themselves
OL,15,Fby going on some courses and doing
OL,16,Fsome training."
